Southwestern Electric Power Company
Southwestern Electric Power Company (SWEPCO) serves 520,400 customers in Louisiana, Arkansas, East Texas and the Panhandle area of North Texas. We are committed to helping our residential and commercial customers save energy and money. SWEPCO is part of the American Electric Power system, which is one of the largest electric utilities in the United States, delivering electricity to more than 5 million customers in 11 states.
