2015 ENERGY STAR Award Winners

Congratulations!
Each year, EPA honors a select group of organizations that have made outstanding contributions to protecting the environment through superior energy efficiency. Whether a first time Partner of the Year winner, or a Sustained Excellence winner, these small and large organizations from across the country are leading the energy efficiency movement. Read on to see how the 2015 ENERGY STAR Award winners are helping millions of individuals, families, and businesses save energy and protect the climate. 























Award Winners
The 2015 ENERGY STAR Award Winners lead their industries in the production and sale of energy-efficient products and services, and in the development and adoption of world-class strategies that provide substantial energy and money savings in the buildings where we live and work. The winners have been chosen from a vast network of 16,000 ENERGY STAR partners. To check out their accomplishments, search by organization name or view the winners by category below.









